{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.480", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Umweltministerin Schulze! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.440", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns den Haushalt kurz anschauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.080", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sehen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.200", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kollegin Lemke hat es erw\u00e4hnt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Klimakrise spitzt sich jeden Tag zu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.040", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber die Bundesregierung tritt angesichts dieser Bedrohung einfallslos auf der Stelle: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.040", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stillstand bei der Nationalen Klimaschutzinitiative, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beim Aktionsprogramm Klimaschutz\u00a02020 und beim Klimaschutzplan\u00a02050. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.400", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch dort bleiben die Mittel bei 8\u00a0Millionen Euro stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Klimaschutzplan w\u00e4re \u00fcbrigens ein guter Plan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.640", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie ihn denn umsetzen w\u00fcrden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.560", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir sehen nicht nur Stillstand, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern mit Blick auf den Energie- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.000", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Klimafonds sogar R\u00fcckschritte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.280", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind Milliarden Euros, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.680", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir sofort f\u00fcr Energieeffizienz und erneuerbare W\u00e4rme einsetzen k\u00f6nnten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und was machen Sie? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.280", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie lassen dieses Geld einfach ungenutzt liegen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.280", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Stillstand und dieser R\u00fcckschritt machen nicht einmal haushaltspolitisch Sinn. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie spielen mit dem Feuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.640", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber uns h\u00e4ngen drohend die europ\u00e4ischen Strafzahlungen f\u00fcr das Nichterreichen der deutschen Klimaschutzziele. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben das auf meine Anfrage hin zugegeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.960", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben es im Umweltausschuss zugegeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger werden in Zukunft zahlen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.600", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden hier von einer Summe zwischen 200\u00a0Millionen und 1\u00a0Milliarde Euro."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.720", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Haushalt birgt Stagnation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.520", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "R\u00fcckschritt und Gefahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und warum? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weil Sie als Regierung in Sachen Klimaschutz der Gesellschaft hinterherhinken. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.120", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Handwerkerin baut Solarmodule aufs Schuldach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die B\u00fcrgergenossenschaft plant einen Windpark. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man k\u00f6nnte jetzt meinen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Industrie in Deutschland sei der gr\u00f6\u00dfte Hemmschuh beim Klimaschutz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber nein: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind es. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbst der Bundesverband der Deutschen Industrie sagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.080", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Einhaltung der Klimaziele uns Wirtschaftswachstum bringt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.840", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einzelne Unternehmen fordern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.600", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass endlich die belohnt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.320", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die weniger CO 2 aussto\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich etwas einfallen lassen und effizienter sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie fordern Wettbewerbsanreize."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.000", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss sich das als Marathon vorstellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommunen und gro\u00dfe Teile der Wirtschaft sehen die Chancen des Klimaschutzes und laufen f\u00fcr ihn hei\u00df. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und die Bundesregierung steht am Rand auf der Zuschauertrib\u00fcne und schaut sich das an. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.680", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und nicht nur das: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.600", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wirft den Laufenden auch noch Hindernisse in den Weg.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.240", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Ministerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jetzt werden Sie sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.280", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich laufe doch mit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.200", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe doch die Vorschl\u00e4ge gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.760", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beispielsweise zu einer CO 2 -Abgabe.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wissen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.760", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mein gr\u00fcnes Herz schl\u00e4gt ja h\u00f6her, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.360", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie sich gr\u00fcne Forderungen aneignen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.560", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen eine CO 2 -Abgabe einf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.040", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind f\u00fcr die Nachr\u00fcstung der Diesel\u00adskandalautos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind f\u00fcr die Nachr\u00fcstung aller Schiffsmotoren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie brennen ein Feuerwerk an Forderungen ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dann werden Sie von Ihren eigenen Kollegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.320", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was eigentlich?\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht einmal ausgebremst: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.600", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es h\u00f6rt Ihnen einfach keiner zu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "leider."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo Sie selbst handeln k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.680", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "federf\u00fchrend im Umweltministerium, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.200", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da haben Sie teilweise etwas getan. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das eigentlich f\u00fcr 2020 angek\u00fcndigte Programm zur Entkarbonisierung der Stahl- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Zementindustrie werden Sie vorziehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Schritt in die richtige Richtung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber bitte unterst\u00fctzen Sie nicht nur die Industrie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.040", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch die Verbraucherin und den Verbraucher,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Sie interessanterweise f\u00fcr unvern\u00fcnftig halten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.000", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Bericht zu den gestiegenen Treibhausgasemissionen im Verkehr schreiben Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Personenverkehr kann dies auch auf den Trend zu leistungsst\u00e4rkeren und schwereren Pkws zur\u00fcckgef\u00fchrt werden.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.320", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einfach ausgedr\u00fcckt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.560", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verbraucherinnen und Verbraucher sind schuld. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.200", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie fahren mehr SUVs. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.360", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie kaufen weiterhin Benzinautos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.600", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das tun sie zwar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.680", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber haben Sie schon einmal Ihre Energiebesteuerung genauer angeschaut? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.720", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer schmutzige Energie tankt und verheizt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.960", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wird vom Staat sogar noch belohnt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.800", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn der Staat schon mitverdient am Energieverbrauch der B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.000", 
   "id": "s000089", 
